title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Jun 18 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Jun 18 2022
description:
Republican Mayra Flores wins special election victory in Democrat Texas district in major sign of a Red Tsunami coming in November. Clay says, "We're talking about seats that nobody even considered being in play. Maybe the biggest Red Wave of all time potentially on the horizon." Biden administration to punish border control agents who were CLEARED of accusations they whipped migrants. The View endorses Kamala/Pete ticket to beat Trump or "DeathSantis." Democrats can't win a contest of ideas, so they cling to identity politics.
